Sustainability Accounting Standards Board ("SASB") Disclosures
SASB published the Sustainability Accounting Standard ("Standard") for the Real Estate Industry in October 2018. Equinix has
aligned its SASB disclosures with the Real Estate Standard to enhance corporate disclosure around ESG performance. In our
comprehensive disclosures in our annual Corporate Sustainability Report we also document our progress against metrics as
outlined in other frameworks such as the Global Reporting Initiative ("GRI"), UN Sustainable Development Goals ("SDGs") and the
Task Force on Climate-related Financial Disclosures ("TCFD"). The following tables detail our energy metrics, aligned with the
SASB Real Estate Standard. We intend to expand our reporting around the Real Estate Standard in the future.
