our back office systems and investments to maintain our qualification for taxation as a REIT and to integrate recent acquisitions.
We also expect travel and entertainment expenses to increase once travel restrictions that were imposed in response to the
COVID-19 pandemic are reduced. Additionally, given that our corporate headquarters is located within the U.S., we expect
