redemption premium that was paid in cash and $1.3 million related to the write-off of unamortized debt issuance costs.
1.250% Senior Notes due 2025, 1.800% Senior Notes due 2027, 2.150% Senior Notes due 2030, and 3.000% Senior Notes due
