"2025 Notes"), $500.0 million aggregate principal amount of 1.800% senior notes due 2027 (the "2027 Notes"), $1.1 billion
aggregate principal amount of 2.150% senior notes due 2030 (the "2030 Notes"), and $500.0 million aggregate principal amount
of 3.000% senior notes due 2050 (the "2050 Notes"). Interest on these notes is payable semi-annually on January 15 and July 15
