During the year ended December 31, 2020, the Company recorded $145.8 million of loss on debt extinguishment primarily
comprised of:
•$5.9 million of loss on debt extinguishment from the redemption of the 2022 Notes, which included $4.6 million redemption
premium that was paid in cash and $1.3 million related to the write-off of unamortized debt issuance costs.(1) (2)
