•$17.1 million of loss on debt extinguishment as a result of amendments to leases impacting the related financing
obligations;
•$19.5 million of loss on debt extinguishment from the settlement of financing obligations as a result of the Infomart Dallas
Acquisition;
•$12.6 million of loss on debt extinguishment as a result of the settlement of financing obligations for properties purchased;
and
•$2.2 million of loss on debt extinguishment as a result of the redemption of the Japanese Yen Term Loan.
